Content: @Egor Lukyanchenko I don't see how extending the shapes would change anything.  I mean you could extend their area and then add them to the "gate" part of the `antenna_check` and not use the `diode` function at all ...

Content: @Tholin It's just different ... if the gate area is < 1 um^2 it'll be more strict and if gate area is > 1 um^2 then it's more lenient.
